text: Læa ha kxallxhˌ ca thrng xea thosʹ mnusʹy tam thi phwk khea di khwnkhway xea wi læw phraxngkh ca mi thrng hı helux wi bn hna phændin sung satw lok tang «tæwa phraxngkh thrng prawing wela hı phwk khea cnthung wela thi thuk kahnd wi khran meux wara kahnd khxng phwk khea di ma thung meux nan hæla thæ cring xallxhˌ pen phuthrng hen pwng baw khxng phraxngkh semx
